tags.name:
csv-render
`Remote render a CSV file in place as an accessible table.`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `csv-render`
 * @customElement csv-render
 * `Remote render a CSV file in place as an accessible table.`
 *
 * @microcopy - language worth noting:
 *  - CSV is comma separated values
 *

 * @demo ./demo/index.html
 */

attributes.name: data-source
attributes.description: Location of the CSV file.

attributes.name: caption
attributes.description: Caption for the table to improve accessibility and readability.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.description: Summary to improve accessibility for screen readers.

attributes.name: table
attributes.description: Table busted out as an array.

attributes.name: tableHeadings
attributes.description: Headings from the first row of the csv

attributes.name: table-data
attributes.description: Raw data pulled in from the csv file.

attributes.name: color
attributes.description: Color class work to apply

properties.name: tableHeadings
